    "_scoring_notes": "Scoring: The EDE, and its self-reported versions, EDE-Q, generate two types of data. First they provide frequency data on key behavioral features of eating disorders in terms of number of episodes of the behavior and in some instances number of days on which the behavior has occurred. Second, they provide subscale scores reflecting the severity of aspects of the psychopathology of eating disorders. The subscales are Restraint, Eating Concern, Shape Concern and Weight Concern. To obtain a particular subscale score, the ratings for the relevant items (listed below) are added together and the sum divided by the total number of items forming the subscales. If ratings are only available on some items, a score may nevertheless be obtained by dividing the resulting total by the number of rated items so long as more than half the items have been rated. To obtain an overall or \"global\" score, the four subscales scores are summed and the resulting total divided by the number of subscales (i.e. four). Subscales score are reported as means and standard deviations."
  },
  "translations": {
    "en": {
      "info_230104": "Eating Disorder Examination Questionnaire � (EDE-Q 6.0) Instructions: The following questions are concerned with the past four weeks (28 days) only. Please read each question carefully. Please answer all the questions. Thank you.Questions 1 to 12: Please select the appropriate answer on the right. Remember that the questions only refer to the past four weeks (28 days) only.",
      "psychopathologyquestionnaire_limit_foodinstake_influence_weightshape": "On how many of the past 28 days, have you been deliberately trying to limit the amount of food you eat to influence your shape or weight (whether or not you have succeeded)?",
      "psychopathologyquestionnaire_limit_foodinstake_influence_weightshape_opt_0": "No days",
      "psychopathologyquestionnaire_limit_foodinstake_influence_weightshape_opt_1": "1-5 days",
      "psychopathologyquestionnaire_limit_foodinstake_influence_weightshape_opt_2": "6-12 days",
      "psychopathologyquestionnaire_limit_foodinstake_influence_weightshape_opt_3": "13-15 days",
      "psychopathologyquestionnaire_limit_foodinstake_influence_weightshape_opt_4": "16-22 days",
      "psychopathologyquestionnaire_limit_foodinstake_influence_weightshape_opt_5": "23-27 days",
      "psychopathologyquestionnaire_limit_foodinstake_influence_weightshape_opt_6": "every day",
      "psychopathologyquestionnaire_longperiods_fasting_influence_weightshape": "On how many of the past 28 days, have you gone for long periods of time (8 waking hours or more) without eating anything at all in order to influence your shape or weight?",
      "psychopathologyquestionnaire_longperiods_fasting_influence_weightshape_opt_0": "No days",
      "psychopathologyquestionnaire_longperiods_fasting_influence_weightshape_opt_1": "1-5 days",
      "psychopathologyquestionnaire_longperiods_fasting_influence_weightshape_opt_2": "6-12 days",
      "psychopathologyquestionnaire_longperiods_fasting_influence_weightshape_opt_3": "13-15 days",
      "psychopathologyquestionnaire_longperiods_fasting_influence_weightshape_opt_4": "16-22 days",
      "psychopathologyquestionnaire_longperiods_fasting_influence_weightshape_opt_5": "23-27 days",
      "psychopathologyquestionnaire_longperiods_fasting_influence_weightshape_opt_6": "every day",
      "psychopathologyquestionnaire_dietaryrestrictions_influence_weightshape": "On how many of the past 28 days, have you tried to exclude from your diet any foods that you like in order to influence your shape or weight (whether or not you have succeeded)?",
      "psychopathologyquestionnaire_dietaryrestrictions_influence_weightshape_opt_0": "No days",
      "psychopathologyquestionnaire_dietaryrestrictions_influence_weightshape_opt_1": "1-5 days",
      "psychopathologyquestionnaire_dietaryrestrictions_influence_weightshape_opt_2": "6-12 days",
      "psychopathologyquestionnaire_dietaryrestrictions_influence_weightshape_opt_3": "13-15 days",
      "psychopathologyquestionnaire_dietaryrestrictions_influence_weightshape_opt_4": "16-22 days",
      "psychopathologyquestionnaire_dietaryrestrictions_influence_weightshape_opt_5": "23-27 days",
      "psychopathologyquestionnaire_dietaryrestrictions_influence_weightshape_opt_6": "every day",
      "psychopathologyquestionnaire_dietaryrules_influence_weightshape": "On how many of the past 28 days, have you tried to follow definite rules regarding your eating (for example, a calorie limit) in order to influence your shape or weight (whether or not you have succeeded)?",
      "psychopathologyquestionnaire_dietaryrules_influence_weightshape_opt_0": "No days",
      "psychopathologyquestionnaire_dietaryrules_influence_weightshape_opt_1": "1-5 days",
      "psychopathologyquestionnaire_dietaryrules_influence_weightshape_opt_2": "6-12 days",
      "psychopathologyquestionnaire_dietaryrules_influence_weightshape_opt_3": "13-15 days",
      "psychopathologyquestionnaire_dietaryrules_influence_weightshape_opt_4": "16-22 days",
      "psychopathologyquestionnaire_dietaryrules_influence_weightshape_opt_5": "23-27 days",
      "psychopathologyquestionnaire_dietaryrules_influence_weightshape_opt_6": "every day",
      "psychopathologyquestionnaire_emptystomach_influence_weightshape": "On how many of the past 28 days, have you had a definite desire to have any empty stomach with the aim of influencing your shape or weight?",
      "psychopathologyquestionnaire_emptystomach_influence_weightshape_opt_0": "No days",
      "psychopathologyquestionnaire_emptystomach_influence_weightshape_opt_1": "1-5 days",
      "psychopathologyquestionnaire_emptystomach_influence_weightshape_opt_2": "6-12 days",
      "psychopathologyquestionnaire_emptystomach_influence_weightshape_opt_3": "13-15 days",
      "psychopathologyquestionnaire_emptystomach_influence_weightshape_opt_4": "16-22 days",
      "psychopathologyquestionnaire_emptystomach_influence_weightshape_opt_5": "23-27 days",
      "psychopathologyquestionnaire_emptystomach_influence_weightshape_opt_6": "every day",
      "psychopathologyquestionnaire_desire_flat_stomach": "On how many of the past 28 days, have you had a definite desire to have a totally flat stomach?",
      "psychopathologyquestionnaire_desire_flat_stomach_opt_0": "No days",
      "psychopathologyquestionnaire_desire_flat_stomach_opt_1": "1-5 days",
      "psychopathologyquestionnaire_desire_flat_stomach_opt_2": "6-12 days",
      "psychopathologyquestionnaire_desire_flat_stomach_opt_3": "13-15 days",
      "psychopathologyquestionnaire_desire_flat_stomach_opt_4": "16-22 days",
      "psychopathologyquestionnaire_desire_flat_stomach_opt_5": "23-27 days",
      "psychopathologyquestionnaire_desire_flat_stomach_opt_6": "every day",
      "psychopathologyquestionnaire_thinkingfoodeating_distraction": "On how many of the past 28 days, has thinking about food, eating, or calories made it very difficult to concentrate on things you are interested in (for example, working, following a conversation, or reading)?",
      "psychopathologyquestionnaire_thinkingfoodeating_distraction_opt_0": "No days",
      "psychopathologyquestionnaire_thinkingfoodeating_distraction_opt_1": "1-5 days",
      "psychopathologyquestionnaire_thinkingfoodeating_distraction_opt_2": "6-12 days",
      "psychopathologyquestionnaire_thinkingfoodeating_distraction_opt_3": "13-15 days",
      "psychopathologyquestionnaire_thinkingfoodeating_distraction_opt_4": "16-22 days",
      "psychopathologyquestionnaire_thinkingfoodeating_distraction_opt_5": "23-27 days",
      "psychopathologyquestionnaire_thinkingfoodeating_distraction_opt_6": "every day",
      "psychopathologyquestionnaire_thinkingweightshape_distraction": "On how many of the past 28 days, has thinking about shape or weight made it very difficult to concentrate on things you are interested in (for example, working, following a conversation, or reading)?",
      "psychopathologyquestionnaire_thinkingweightshape_distraction_opt_0": "No days",
      "psychopathologyquestionnaire_thinkingweightshape_distraction_opt_1": "1-5 days",
      "psychopathologyquestionnaire_thinkingweightshape_distraction_opt_2": "6-12 days",
